CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Marwynn Holdings is a holding company with no operations other than holding the shares of its two wholly-owned operating subsidiaries, FuAn Enterprise, Inc. and Grand Forest Cabinetry Inc, that are in the supply chain business. Through our subsidiaries, we are committed to becoming a leading supply chain company in the U.S. for food, non-alcoholic beverages and indoor home improvement products.
